children.text: Located in the Grand Lodge Hotel, start your day off with freshly made to order breakfast offerings and espresso drinks. Return after your day exploring for hand tossed pizzas and craft beers in a fun ambient setting.

Enjoy the warm ambiance and culinary excellence of Uley’s Cabin. Serving gourmet Colorado inspired lunches in a warm and comfortable rustic cabin setting. Looking for soemthing more casual then join us outside for signature hot cocoa drinks, elk skweres or Wagyu beef burgers.

The Umbrella Bar at Ten Peaks is located at the top of Painter Boy chairlift. The en-piste bar & restaurant is perfectly situated for beginners and fans of blue groomers to take a break and refuel.It offers postcard-perfect views of the valley and a variety of food options for the whole family.
Quick option for dine-in or take-out. Specializing in fried chicken sandwiches, chicken tenders, fries and vegetarian options too!
Located at the base of Paradise Express, Paradise Warming House is the perfect mid-mountain meeting spot. It’s got all you need to refuel, from drinks and burgers to soups, chili and more!

Fuel up for an epic day on the mountain with coffee and espresso beverages, hot breakfast sandwiches, sweet pastry treats and snacks. Also offering artisan-style sandwiches, soups and grab-and-go salads.
A full-service dining experience with some of the best views of the Butte! The deck is the perfect spot to kick back after a day well spent.
